title: She Thinks She’s Too Ugly And Her Boyfriend Should Be With His Ex?!
description:
Imposter syndrome is a hell of a drug. It makes you think that for whatever reason, you aren’t deserving of where you are, what you’re doing, or who you’re with.
Ramona, a Bert Show listener, is experiencing some imposter syndrome in her relationship and reached out to us for advice.
